Yeah, and I've known him.

35:17.598 --> 35:18.319
They don't have a car.

35:18.339 --> 35:20.462
Well, of course, he's in Toronto.

35:20.502 --> 35:21.484
He doesn't really need to.

35:21.504 --> 35:22.265
