35:22.285 --> 35:23.067
I can walk to anything.

35:23.087 --> 35:24.289
Oh, there are good stores right by.

35:24.389 --> 35:25.090
One doesn't need to do it.

35:25.331 --> 35:27.614
And my wife does drive and have a car.

35:27.634 --> 35:28.596
But I've just avoided...

35:28.998 --> 35:33.823
Anyway, you just avoid a whole dimension of existence which you don't want to get involved with.

35:33.883 --> 35:35.285
Calder is a non-driver also.

35:35.846 --> 35:42.493
And there's a library of 2,000 books 5,000 miles away, and it sounds not too promising.

35:42.553 --> 35:44.876
Well, I just shrug my shoulders and forget it.

35:44.896 --> 35:47.799
I've got enough for a one-man thing.

35:47.859 --> 35:49.401
I also like things that I can deal with.

35:49.441 --> 35:51.744
Cars I don't have no interest in getting greasy and fixing.

